## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- We will execute the scraping script against a generic public Reddit community (e.g. `r/webdev`) to verify Playwright connects, parses the DOM, extracts the raw strings, and assigns the correct priority weight based on our config UI.

### Manual Verification
- Verify the UI in `/settings` persists new topic vectors.
- Verify that live scraped items successfully populate the main dashboard's Inbox feed instead of the dummy mock data.
